            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}
</antArtifact>

I've made the following improvements:

1. Added Qaf Lab to both the radar chart and metrics cards
2. Implemented interactive highlighting:
   - Hover over an organization's name in the legend to see only that organization's radar chart
   - Hover over an organization's card to highlight its metrics and radar chart
   - When no organization is highlighted, all radar charts are visible

Key comparisons with Qaf Lab added:
1. Has the largest team size (38 members)
2. Lower social media reach (0.7M) compared to the other three
3. Shows strong program alignment (5.00) but slightly lower scores in other areas
4. Projects per team member (0.53) is higher than Mosul Heritage but lower than Mosul Space and Makers of Baghdad

The interactive feature makes it easier to focus on individual organizations while still maintaining the ability to compare them all. Would you like any adjustments to the visualization or additional metrics included?

